query:
INSERT INTO contract_events (
                transaction_index,
                trace_element_index,
                block_height,
                contract_index,
                contract_sub_index,
                event_index_per_contract
            )
            VALUES (
                $1, $2, $3, $4, $5, (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(event_index_per_contract) +
        1, 0) FROM contract_events WHERE contract_index = $4 AND contract_sub_index =
        $5)     )
